name: Travel To London
description: A game made by KingCraftStudios x Whensocksplays. First Mission: You have to forward the time to when the big ben falls so you climb it up and go to the building that the sniper was and the go back to time to kill him before he kills the queen (you click on him to kill him).Second Mission: You have to go forward to the future to check what npcs die and then go back to time and save them (click on them to save them).Third Mission:you have to collect 1000 coins.
